name: SQDev
tagline: The eclipse plugin for SQF support
body:
###Welcome in the world of SQDev
SQDev is a plugin for [eclipse](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eclipse_%28software%29) that will teach it how to support SQF. Therefore all the features of a modern [IDE](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integrated_development_environment) will be available for you as soon as you have installed the plugin.

###Further information
For further information about this plugin and [how to install](https://github.com/Krzmbrzl/SQDev/wiki/Installation) it you can refer to the [wiki](https://github.com/Krzmbrzl/SQDev/wiki)

###Troubles and bugs
If you have any troubles concerning this plugin you can contact me @Krzmbrzl and I will see what I can do for you.
If you encounter any bugs please [create an issue](https://github.com/Krzmbrzl/SQDev/issues) to let me know about it so I can fix it.

###Feature requests
I am open for all kind of feature requests. If you have one you can as well [create an issue](https://github.com/Krzmbrzl/SQDev/issues) and I will see what I can do
